sequenceDiagram
    participant Pay as 支付回调
    participant Cancel as 超时取消消费者
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    par 并发执行
        Pay->>DB: UPDATE status=PAID<br/>WHERE status=CREATED
        Cancel->>DB: UPDATE status=CANCELING<br/>WHERE status=CREATED
    end

    alt 支付先取得行锁并提交
        DB-->>Pay: affected_rows=1
        DB-->>Cancel: affected_rows=0
        Note over Cancel: 查询发现已 PAID，幂等结束
    else 取消先取得行锁并提交
        DB-->>Cancel: affected_rows=1
        DB-->>Pay: affected_rows=0
        Note over Pay: 记录晚到支付并触发退款
    end
